  "body": "Four memos from thingalog-strategist between 2026-05-22 and 2026-05-23 carry OAGP-pattern-shape work that is properly oagp-strategist scope. They were filed in orgdef-spec/memos/ before the data-vs-pattern distinction was sharpened (last memo in the chain is itself the sharpening + correction). Per addendum §4 recommendation (b) — preserve history-where-history-was-made; link from where the work actually belongs — these memos remain in orgdef-spec; this memo is the cross-reference pointer for the oagp-strategist inbox. Read in order. Three are action-required at their source filing; the fourth re-categorizes them. When you take over: (a) all four are addressed structurally to orgdef-strategist but substantively to your seat (post-sharpening); (b) decision artifacts I drafted while still holding the work in orgdef-spec are now withdrawn — see the companion inbox-pointers memo for those input artifacts.",
